<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Express Entry Cutoff History 2015–2026 — Every CRS Draw Score, Lowest Ever &amp; 2026 Trends</h1>
    <p>Complete Express Entry CRS cutoff score history from the first draw in January 2015 through April 2026. See the lowest score ever (413), highest score (875 — PNP tie-breaking), yearly averages, category-based draw trends, and what CRS score you need in 2026.</p>
    <div class="pill-row">
      <span class="pill">Updated April 2026</span>
      <span class="pill">All Draw Types Covered</span>
      <span class="pill">Lowest Ever: 413 (Nov 2019)</span>
      <span class="pill">2026 Average: ~491</span>
      <span class="pill">Searchable Draw Table</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="https://crsscorecalculator.vercel.app/" class="btn btn-white">Calculate My CRS Score →</a>
      <a href="#draw-history" class="btn btn-outline">View Full Draw History</a>
    </div>
